  <div class="one-third column">
    <h4 class="myheadings">YSP Sound Projection &gt;&gt;</h4>
    <div class="thecontent">
      <table border="1" cellpadding="0" cellspacing="10" width="100%">
        <tr>
          <td class="incompatible">YAS-101</td>
          <td class="incompatible">YAS-201</td>
          <td class="incompatible">YHT-S401</td>
        </tr>
        <tr>
          <td class="compatible">YSP-2200</td>
          <td class="compatible">YSP-3300</td>
          <td class="compatible">YSP-4300</td>
        </tr>
        <tr>
          <td class="compatible">YSP-4100</td>
          <td class="compatible">YSP-5100</td>
          <td></td>
        </tr>
      </table>
      <br>
      <p>For years Yamaha has maintained its position at the forefront of front surround technology. The Yamaha Sound Projector range pioneered true 5.1 channel surround sound from a single unit. Now, Yamaha pushes the envelope in digital sound projector technology with immersive 7.1 channel surround sound from a single sound bar solution. This is achieved by bouncing ‘beams’ of sound off walls or hard surfaces to produce a true multi-channel surround sound experience like no other manufacturer in the market.</p>
      <p>The included microphone calibrates the sound to direct these beams to bounce off various surfaces, producing industry-leading surround sound from a sound bar product. For the best in sound bar technology, look no further than a YSP sound bar.</p>
      <p><img src="images/ysp-technology.jpg" width="100%" ></p>
    </div>
    <h4 class="myheadings">Air Surround Extreme &gt;&gt;</h4>
    <div class="thecontent">
      <table border="1" cellpadding="0" cellspacing="10" width="100%">
        <tr>
          <td class="compatible">YAS-101</td>
          <td class="compatible">YAS-201</td>
          <td class="compatible">YHT-S401</td>
        </tr>
        <tr>
          <td class="incompatible">YSP-2200</td>
          <td class="incompatible">YSP-3300</td>
          <td class="incompatible">YSP-4300</td>
        </tr>
        <tr>
          <td class="incompatible">YSP-4100</td>
          <td class="incompatible">YSP-5100</td>
          <td></td>
        </tr>
      </table>
      <br>
      <p>Yamaha’s exclusive AIR SURROUND XTREME reproduces 7.1-channel surround sound with high quality, excellent imaging and rich presence. It uses the ears natural ability to determine sound direction to ensure a realistic surround field.</p>
      <p>You’ll experience an extremely realistic and impressive sound field, with clear dialogue in the front and dynamic sound action at the back and sides.</p>
      <p><img src="images/asx.jpg" width="100%" ></p>
    </div>
    <h4 class="myheadings">TV Audio Booster &gt;&gt;</h4>
    <div class="thecontent">
      <table border="1" cellpadding="0" cellspacing="10" width="100%">
        <tr>
          <td class="compatible">YAS-101</td>
          <td class="compatible">YAS-201</td>
          <td class="incompatible">YHT-S401</td>
        </tr>
        <tr>
          <td class="incompatible">YSP-2200</td>
          <td class="incompatible">YSP-3300</td>
          <td class="incompatible">YSP-4300</td>
        </tr>
        <tr>
          <td class="incompatible">YSP-4100</td>
