      <br>
      <p>With televisions becoming thinner, audio quality is typically sacrificed due to smaller speaker enclosures.</p>
      <p>A Yamaha TV Booster sound bar is a simple and affordable solution to providing significantly improved audio for TV viewing and something that should be considered with every flat screen TV.</p>
      <p><img src="images/tv-booster.jpg" width="100%" ></p>
    </div>
    <h4 class="myheadings">HD Audio &gt;&gt;</h4>
    <div class="thecontent">
      <table border="1" cellpadding="0" cellspacing="10" width="100%">
        <tr>
          <td class="incompatible">YAS-101</td>
          <td class="incompatible">YAS-201</td>
          <td class="compatible">YHT-S401</td>
        </tr>
        <tr>
          <td class="compatible">YSP-2200</td>
          <td class="compatible">YSP-3300</td>
          <td class="compatible">YSP-4300</td>
        </tr>
        <tr>
          <td class="compatible">YSP-4100</td>
          <td class="compatible">YSP-5100</td>
          <td></td>
        </tr>
      </table>
      <br>
      <p>HD Audio, also known as ‘lossless’ audio, refers to audio that sounds identical to the original studio master recording and is found on Blu-ray discs.</p>
      <p>Dolby and DTS each have their own versions of this ‘lossless’ format, such as Dolby TrueHD and DTS-HD Master Audio.</p>
      <p>These formats deliver a truly amazing surround sound experience, akin to the audio quality experienced in a movie theatre.</p>
      <p><img src="images/hd-audio.jpg" width="100%" ></p>
    </div>
  </div>
  <div class="one-third column">
    <h4 class="myheadings">Compressed Music Enhancer &gt;&gt;</h4>
    <div class="thecontent">
      <table border="1" cellpadding="0" cellspacing="10" width="100%">
        <tr>
          <td class="incompatible">YAS-101</td>
          <td class="compatible">YAS-201</td>
          <td class="compatible">YHT-S401</td>
        </tr>
        <tr>
          <td class="compatible">YSP-2200</td>
          <td class="compatible">YSP-3300</td>
          <td class="compatible">YSP-4300</td>
        </tr>
        <tr>
          <td class="compatible">YSP-4100</td>
          <td class="compatible">YSP-5100</td>
          <td></td>
        </tr>
      </table>
      <br>
      <p>Some popular digital music formats (such as MP3) are compressed in file size, minimising storage requirements.</p>
      <p>This compression of data often results in diminished sound quality. To combat this, Yamaha’s Compressed Music Enhancer uses algorithms to restore this lost sonic information to bring back the groove of the original recording.</p>
      <p><img src="images/compressed.jpg" width="100%" ></p>
    </div>
    <h4 class="myheadings">Built-in subwoofer &gt;&gt;</h4>
    <div class="thecontent">
      <table border="1" cellpadding="0" cellspacing="10" width="100%">
        <tr>
          <td class="compatible">YAS-101</td>
          <td class="incompatible">YAS-201</td>
          <td class="incompatible">YHT-S401</td>
        </tr>
        <tr>
          <td class="incompatible">YSP-2200</td>
          <td class="incompatible">YSP-3300</td>
          <td class="incompatible">YSP-4300</td>
        </tr>
        <tr>
          <td class="incompatible">YSP-4100</td>
          <td class="incompatible">YSP-5100</td>
          <td></td>
        </tr>
      </table>
      <br>
      <p>Instead of having a separate subwoofer, Yamaha have cut down the space required by building the subwoofer into the sound bar. This allows you to experience the deep rumblings of your movie without a subwoofer taking up additional space in the lounge room.</p>
      <p>The YAS-101 combines two 6.5 cm cone speakers with a dual driver subwoofer driven by a digital amp with a total output of 120W. Although compact, its excellent structural design provides a large volume enclosure for both the speakers and subwoofer.</p>
      <p>The result is powerful, high quality sound that enhances audio from TV and movies. The dual-driver subwoofer employs large magnets and large-diameter voice coils to realise dynamic and robust bass reproduction, ensuring the overall sound has a rich sense of presence.</p>
      <p><img src="images/built-in-sub.jpg" width="100%" ></p>
    </div>
