      <br>
      <p>UniVolume manipulates the level of volume so that more even listening is maintained.</p>
      <p>The volume of the TV can be limited so that it will not increase suddenly whenever louder content such as commercials are broadcast (a handy feature).</p>
      <p><img src="images/univolume.jpg" width="100%" ></p>
