      <p>A key advantage of the sound bar range is its ability to minimise clutter - eliminating the need for surround speakers and cables throughout the room.</p>
      <p>A wireless subwoofer system takes this a step further by offering even greater flexibility in positioning. Experience tight and deep bass while enjoying the versatility of being able to place the subwoofer anywhere in the room.</p>
